    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Jiraiya's Synthetic Human Clan Level 8+<br />You extend your contract to more exotic toads, capable of molding diferent elements. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>You select between Lightning Release and Wind Release. You are now able to add jutsu with the corresponding Nature Release to your jutsu list.</li><li>Toads that you summon gain access to Jutsus with the corresponding Nature Release</li><li>You learn one jutsu with the corresponding Nature Release that you selected, that you qualify for.</li><li>You can take this feat twice, selecting the nature release that you did not select the first time.</li></ul>",
